Authorization: Bearer {{A_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### 각자 위치 보고 TEST API - B 위치 보고
POST http://localhost:7777/v1/driving/team/test/location/{{B_RIDING_RECORD_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{B_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

